               </font></Label>
            <Label layoutX="34.0" layoutY="390.0" prefHeight="60.0" prefWidth="1499.0" styleClass="rules" stylesheets="@application.css" text="⚫ The objective of the game is to kill as many monsters as possible.">
               <font>
                  <Font name="System Italic" size="12.0" />
               </font>
